{"TopicId":15626,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Wing Walking","CreatedByName":"Fuzzy Dunlop","CreatedById":27329,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T01:21:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fuzzy Dunlop","CreatedById":27329,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T01:21:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOne of my aeroplanes is stable enough to fly without any control imput - if you trim it right it just stays at 5000m flying in huge 400km circles. During a test flight I accidently (honestly it \u003Cem\u003Ewas\u003C/em\u003E an accident) sent Bill on a EVA. Instead of falling straight to his death he ended up wedged in the tail of my plane.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28639;image\u0022 alt=\u0022index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28639;image\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHe finally came loose a few minutes later but this gave me an idea.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28641;image\u0022 alt=\u0022index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28641;image\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI added a network of ladders and now the Kerbals can crawl about during flight:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28643;image\u0022 alt=\u0022index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28643;image\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBuilding ladders on wings is suprisingly difficult, and returing to the cockpit is hard. Usually something like this happens:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28645;image\u0022 alt=\u0022index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28645;image\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T02:04:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf it was really an accident, why did you just happen to have ladders all over the outside of the plane? I think the authorities need to look into Bill\\\u0027s demise. \u0026gt;\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheBlaster","CreatedById":10575,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T03:12:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe first picture has no ladders...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DayOne","CreatedById":20886,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T03:23:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EUse folding ladders. They are longer and weigh the same.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso I now have to try this. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fuzzy Dunlop","CreatedById":27329,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-30T23:08:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DayOne\u0022 data-cite=\u0022DayOne\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUse folding ladders. They are longer and weigh the same.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso I now have to try this. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGood idea, now I made it to the wingtip!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28770;image\u0022 alt=\u0022index.php?action=dlattach;topic=17512.0;attach=28770;image\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}